{
  "text": "tumor suppressor. [CITATION_1] In the current study, we examined the expression of NR5A2 in tissues samples from PDAC patients in association with tumor characteristics and overall survival. We further investigated the possible molecular mechanisms that linking NR5A2 with PDAC.",
